∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : LinearOrderedField R] (n k : ℕ) (s : Multiset R),
  SupSet.sSup (Set.range (λ s, Multiset.esymm s k / (Multiset.esymm s 1) ^ k)) = 1 / Nat.factorial k

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : LinearOrderedField R] {n k : ℕ} (s : Multiset R),
  s.card = n →
    iSup (fun a : Multiset R =>
      Multiset.esymm a k / (Multiset.esymm a 1) ^ k) = 1 / Nat.factorial k

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : LinearOrderedField R] (k : ℕ),
  iSup (fun (s : Multiset R) => Multiset.esymm s k / (Multiset.esymm s 1) ^ k) = 1 / (Nat.factorial k)

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : CommSemiring R] (k : ℕ) (s : Multiset R),
  let s_k := Multiset.esymm s k
  let s_1 := Multiset.esymm s 1
  let M_k := iSup (fun (a : R) => s_k / s_1 ^ k)
  (∀ (a₁ a₂ : R), M_k = 1 / (Nat.factorial k : R))

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : LinearOrder R] [inst_1 : CommSemiring R] [inst_2 : SupSet R] (k : ℕ),
  (iSup fun (a : Multiset R) => (Multiset.esymm a k) / (Multiset.esymm a 1) ^ k) = 1 / (Nat.factorial k)

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : LinearOrderedField R] (n k : ℕ),
  (⨆ (s : Multiset R), Multiset.esymm s k / (Multiset.esymm s 1) ^ k) = 1 / Nat.factorial k

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : LinearOrderedField R] {n k : ℕ} {s : Multiset R},
  let sk := Multiset.esymm s k in
  let s1k := Multiset.esymm s 1 ^ k in
  SupSet.sSup {x : R | ∃ (a : Fin n → R), x = sk / s1k} = 1 / Nat.factorial k

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : LinearOrderedField R] {n k : ℕ} (a : Fin n → R),
  iSup (fun a => Multiset.esymm (Multiset.map a Finset.univ.val) k / Multiset.esymm (Multiset.map a Finset.univ.val) 1 ^ k) = 1 / ↑(Nat.factorial k)

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : LinearOrderedField R] (n k : ℕ) (s : Multiset R),
  let a := (fun (a : R) => Multiset.esymm s k / Multiset.esymm s 1 ^ k) in
  iSup a = 1 / Nat.factorial k

∀ {R : Type u_1} [inst : LinearOrderedField R] {n k : ℕ} (s : Multiset R),
  (Multiset.card s = n) →
    iSup (fun (a : Multiset R) => (Multiset.esymm a k) / (Multiset.esymm a 1) ^ k) = 1 / (Nat.factorial k)
